	    <div class="article-teaser__overlay">
	        <div class="article-teaser__text">
	        	<div class="inner">
	            	Though nowadays Qatar is well-known for its immense natural oil and gas reserves and the rapid modernisation of society, it has a rich heritage of music and dance intimately related to pearl-diving, sea trade and Bedouin traditions.	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>
