	    <div class="article-teaser__overlay">
	        <div class="article-teaser__text">
	        	<div class="inner">
	            	Wherever European navies sailed, they introduced their own designs of ships and adapted those they saw being used locally. This is the second article in a series of three by the author, providing context and explanation for nautical terminology in the India Office Records.	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>
