	        <div class="article-teaser__text">
	        	<div class="inner">
	            	In the tempestuous history of the British Residency at Mocha, one of the most notable incidents was the bombardment of the city in December 1820. This followed allegations from British officials and Arab leaders of shocking misconduct on both sides.	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>
	</div>
